run_combine_stripe_runs - for list of stripe (internal) calls
			  combine_stripe_runs
combine_stripe_runs - for input stripe, finds the runs and makes the source
		      catalogs for that run (can turn this off) and runs
		      combine_stripe
combine_stripe - combines all the input runs into one single stripe

( ../combine_stripes/combine_stripes.pro - combine multiple stripe files )
